textBox.richText: The storms have returned! Tuesday AM brought 11” to WP, followed by another 11” on Thursday and 14” on Friday. With the big game on Sunday, everyone was heading up for Saturday. Dropped Max off at comp center Saturday AM, then Alli and I headed straight for Belle. Glorious! Alli bailed; I did another lap in there, and then the Eagle had mechanical issues. Got stuck on the egress for a while before bailing out to Pioneer (which then also had evil lines). Worked my way back to Jane...good snow in the trees over there (Frenchy, Tophers...) Vid below.
